title: Weirdhouse Cinema: Time After Time
itunes:title: Weirdhouse Cinema: Time After Time
description:
In this episode of Weirdhouse Cinema, Rob and Joe discuss 1979’s “Time After Time,” in which Jack the Ripper steals H.G. Wells’ time machine and travels to modern San Francisco.
